doc.after: Space exploration is the ongoing discovery and exploration of celestial structures in outer space by means of continuously evolving and growing space technology While the study of space is carried out mainly by astronomers with telescopes the physical exploration of space is conducted both by unmanned robotic probes and human spaceflight
